narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Yes, the professor went out of his way to make personal contacts and resources available as well. There was nothing that could not be achieved with the support and guidance of the T.A and the professor.
Yes, only basic computer programs were required, and those were available.
